ActCanada Customs and Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of ROD MALCOLM of Iqaluit, Nunavut, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Customs and Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of William Grant Hinchey, whose term has expired.
